# Log level (optional)
RUST_LOG=gemini_co_cli=debug,tower_http=debug

# Google Gemini API Key (Optional - for API key authentication)
# Get your API key from: https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
# GEMINI_API_KEY=your_api_key_here

# Authentication Options:
#
# Option 1 - API Key (Simpler):
#   Set GEMINI_API_KEY above, then start the application
#   No additional authentication steps needed
#
# Option 2 - Login with Google (Recommended):
#   Run the container interactively: docker run -it <container-name> gemini
#   Select "Login with Google" from the menu
#   Follow browser authentication prompts
#   Credentials are cached for future sessions
#
# For local development:
#   npm install -g @google/gemini-cli
#   gemini  # Then select "Login with Google"
